    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]

""SELECT [x.ProductColors].[Id], [x.ProductColors].[ColorId], [x.ProductColors].[DateCreated], [x.ProductColors].[DateModified], [x.ProductColors].[ProductId], [x.ProductColors].[Status]
FROM [ProductColor] AS [x.ProductColors]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]
        WHERE [x0].[Status] = 1
        ORDER BY [x0].[DateCreated] DESC, [x0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [x.ProductColors].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[DateCreated] DESC, [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [x.ProductColors].[Id], [x.ProductColors].[ColorId], [x.ProductColors].[DateCreated], [x.ProductColors].[DateModified], [x.ProductColors].[ProductId], [x.ProductColors].[Status]

INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]

""SELECT [x.ProductColors].[Id], [x.ProductColors].[ColorId], [x.ProductColors].[DateCreated], [x.ProductColors].[DateModified], [x.ProductColors].[ProductId], [x.ProductColors].[Status]
FROM [ProductColor] AS [x.ProductColors]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]
        WHERE [x0].[Status] = 1
        ORDER BY [x0].[DateCreated] DESC, [x0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [x.ProductColors].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[DateCreated] DESC, [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [x.ProductColors].[Id], [x.ProductColors].[ColorId], [x.ProductColors].[DateCreated], [x.ProductColors].[DateModified], [x.ProductColors].[ProductId], [x.ProductColors].[Status]
FROM [ProductColor] AS [x.ProductColors]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]

    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]

DECLARE @inserted8 TABLE ([Id] int, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [ProductTag] USING (
VALUES (@p29, @p30, 0),
(@p31, @p32, 1),
(@p33, @p34, 2)) AS i ([ProductId], [TagId], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([ProductId], [TagId])
VALUES (i.[ProductId], i.[TagId])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted8;

    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]

""SELECT [x.ProductColors].[Id], [x.ProductColors].[ColorId], [x.ProductColors].[DateCreated], [x.ProductColors].[DateModified], [x.ProductColors].[ProductId], [x.ProductColors].[Status]
FROM [ProductColor] AS [x.ProductColors]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]
        WHERE [x0].[Status] = 1
        ORDER BY [x0].[DateCreated] DESC, [x0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [x.ProductColors].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[DateCreated] DESC, [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

2018-04-24T13:47:06.1747117+07:00 0HLD9LQH8L81A:00000008 [INF] Executed DbCommand ("0"ms) [Parameters=["@__p_0='?', @__p_1='?'"], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']"
""SELECT [x.ProductColors].[Id], [x.ProductColors].[ColorId], [x.ProductColors].[DateCreated], [x.ProductColors].[DateModified], [x.ProductColors].[ProductId], [x.ProductColors].[Status]
FROM [ProductColor] AS [x.ProductColors]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]
        WHERE [x0].[Status] = 1
        ORDER BY [x0].[DateCreated] DESC, [x0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [x.ProductColors].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[DateCreated] DESC, [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

2018-04-24T13:53:09.6531501+07:00 0HLD9LQH8L81E:00000002 [INF] Executed DbCommand ("6"ms) [Parameters=["@__p_0='?', @__p_1='?'"], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']"
""SELECT [x.ProductColors].[Id], [x.ProductColors].[ColorId], [x.ProductColors].[DateCreated], [x.ProductColors].[DateModified], [x.ProductColors].[ProductId], [x.ProductColors].[Status]
FROM [ProductColor] AS [x.ProductColors]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [x0].[Id], [x0].[DateCreated]
        FROM [Product] AS [x0]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [x.ProductCategory0] ON [x0].[CategoryId] = [x.ProductCategory0].[Id]
        WHERE [x0].[Status] = 1
        ORDER BY [x0].[DateCreated] DESC, [x0].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t]
) AS [t0] ON [x.ProductColors].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[DateCreated] DESC, [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)
